> Whether you have one for breakfast, a post-workout boost, or a quick snack, our ready-to-blend smoothies are just what your body needs! This assortment features three protein-packed flavors: Acai-Cherry Berry, Cocoa Banana Nut, and Tropical Greens. To enjoy one of these no-sugar-added blends, all you have to do is blend them with the liquid of your choice (we like almond or oat milk) until smooth and enjoy! Feel free to add extra protein too, like your favorite whey powder or nut butter.

== Acai-Cherry Berry Smoothies ==

Fill a #cup{} with @liquid of your choice{2%cups} (we recommend @?almond milk{} or @?oat milk{} or water).

Pour @Acai-Cherry Berry Ready-to-Blend Smoothie{2}(frozen) contents into #blender{}; blend until smooth.

Return to the cup and enjoy!

== Cocoa Banana Nut Smoothies ==

Fill a cup with @liquid of your choice{2%cups}.

Pour @Cocoa Banana Nut Ready-to-Blend Smoothie{2}(frozen) contents into blender; blend until smooth.

Return to the cup and enjoy!

== Tropical Greens Smoothies ==

Fill a cup with @liquid of your choice{2%cups}.

Pour @Tropical Greens Ready-to-Blend Smoothie{2}(frozen) contents into blender; blend until smooth.

Return to the cup and enjoy!

> To ensure the highest quality when you receive your smoothies, they will come in a separate box from your meals. Your Ready-to-Blend Smoothie box may arrive a few days after your meal box. Smoothies should be stored frozen.

> Feel free to add extra protein too, like your favorite whey powder or nut butter.

> Download recipe card for complete nutrition, ingredient, and allergen information.